  person("Lisa", "Bottinelli", email = "lisa.bottinelli@gmail.com", role = "ctb"))
Depends:
    R (>= 2.14),
    ggplot2 (>= 2.0.0)
Suggests:
    plyr,
    reshape2,
    testthat,
    data.table,
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
